      "y": 954,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 90,
      "text": "Container: uploads   ·   Blob name = upload UUID\nstageBlock → uncommitted blocks (TTL 7d)\ncommitBlockList → 최종 blob 생성, metadata 유지\nBlob metadata:  x_tus_upload_length,  x_tus_metadata\nAuth: Entra ID (account key 비활성화)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
