      "originalText": "Container: uploads   ·   Blob name = upload UUID\nstageBlock → uncommitted blocks (TTL 7d)\ncommitBlockList → 최종 blob 생성, metadata 유지\nBlob metadata:  x_tus_upload_length,  x_tus_metadata\nAuth: Entra ID (account key 비활성화)",
